libmongo-client
------------------------------------------
This is an alternative C driver for MongoDB, with slightly different goals
than the official one:

libmongo-client is meant to be a stable (API, ABI and quality alike), clean,
well documented and well tested shared library, that strives to make the most
common use cases as convenient as possible.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-1.7.35-1
  libglib2.0-devel-2.42.2-1
  libglib2.0_0-2.42.2-1
  libmongo-client-devel-0.1.8-1bl1
  libmongo-client0-0.1.8-1bl1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  autoconf-13-1
  automake-9-1
  binutils-2.25-1
  cygport-0.18.1-1
  gcc-core-4.9.2-3
  libtool-2.4.6-1
  make-4.1-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/algernon/libmongo-client

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/algernon/libmongo-client/archive/libmongo-client-0.1.8.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack libmongo-client-0.1.8-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./libmongo-client-0.1.8-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/libmongo-client-0.1.8-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libmongo-client-0.1.8-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libmongo-client0-0.1.8-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libmongo-client-devel-0.1.8-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(libmongo-client)
  /usr/bin/mongo-bson-inspect.exe
  /usr/bin/mongo-dump.exe
  /usr/bin/mongo-gridfs.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/libmongo-client.README
  /usr/share/doc/libmongo-client/LICENSE
  /usr/share/doc/libmongo-client/NEWS
  /usr/share/doc/libmongo-client/README.md

(libmongo-client0)
  /usr/bin/cygmongo-client-0.dll

(libmongo-client-devel)
  /usr/include/mongo-client/bson.h
  /usr/include/mongo-client/mongo-client.h
  /usr/include/mongo-client/mongo-sync-cursor.h
  /usr/include/mongo-client/mongo-sync-pool.h
  /usr/include/mongo-client/mongo-sync.h
  /usr/include/mongo-client/mongo-utils.h
  /usr/include/mongo-client/mongo-wire.h
  /usr/include/mongo-client/mongo.h
  /usr/include/mongo-client/sync-gridfs-chunk.h
  /usr/include/mongo-client/sync-gridfs-stream.h
  /usr/include/mongo-client/sync-gridfs.h
  /usr/lib/libmongo-client.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/libmongo-client.pc

